text: The Antonov An-2 is a Soviet airliner & cargo aircraft. It was designed and built after World War II. It is a biplane. It can carry between nine and eleven passengers. NATO calls it Colt. It was built under licence in China as Y-5. It is a single-engine aircraft. == Variants == * Antonov An-3 Category:Soviet & Russian aircraft Category:Soviet military aircraft
title: Antonov An-2
